works.description:
The album, in tree's Gallery, named My  
Alan Dart Patterns, contains 47 images of copyrighted knitted toy
patterns,  
stolen from Alan Dart's website, and used without permission. These are  
being used as a catalogue so that other members can request that they be  

emailed the whole pattern, as an 'exchange'. This infringes Alan's  
copyright and, by making the patterns available in this way, seriously  
affects his income. The url of the album is below.
